sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant PROXY as HTTP Proxy
    participant NODE as Miner Node
    participant TX as Transaction Validator
    participant CHAIN as Chain Manager
    participant PEERS as Peers

    FE ->> PROXY: send signed transaction
    PROXY ->> NODE: forward request
    NODE ->> TX: validate signature and spend plan
    TX -->> NODE: accepted transaction
    NODE ->> CHAIN: queue transaction for inclusion
    NODE ->> PEERS: broadcast mined block
    PEERS -->> NODE: receive and compare branch
    CHAIN -->> NODE: keep longest valid chain
